.TH wxSplitterWindow 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxSplitterWindow \- This class manages up to two subwindows.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The current view can be split into two programmatically (perhaps from a menu command), and unsplit either programmatically or via the \fIwxSplitterWindow\fR user interface.

